937
01:19:43,080 --> 01:19:46,119
<font color="#ffff00"><i>..dan ada banyak mayat bergelimpangan.</i></font>

938
01:19:46,120 --> 01:19:47,639
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Aku menyaksikan sekelompok pemuda..</i></font>

939
01:19:47,640 --> 01:19:48,959
