940
01:19:48,960 --> 01:19:50,879
<font color="#ffff00"><i>..dan mereka menyeret orang-orang..</i></font>

941
01:19:50,880 --> 01:19:53,439
<font color="#ffff00"><i>..dan membunuh mereka di jalan.</i></font>

942
01:19:53,440 --> 01:19:55,839
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Ratusan orang berkumpul di
