948
01:20:07,040 --> 01:20:09,559
<font color="#ffff00"><i>..dan sama sekali tak ada lagi tempat.</i></font>

949
01:20:09,560 --> 01:20:11,039
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Pasar saham bergairah pagi ini,..</i></font>

