958
01:20:34,480 --> 01:20:36,599
<font color="#ffff00"><i>..di Dallas, di Forest Lawn,..</i></font>

959
01:20:36,600 --> 01:20:39,519
<font color="#ffff00"><i>..dan ada 200 orang di alun-alun kota,..</i></font>

960
01:20:39,520 --> 01:20:41,119
<font color="#ffff00"><i>..melakukan Penyucian bersamaan.</i></font>

961
01:20:41,120 --> 01:20:43,519
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Tak pernah kulihat yang seperti ini.</i></font>

